<plot>Embark in a fascinating journey through a Florida few people know. Discover the history of the abandoned island that in the 19th century played the role of today cosmopolitan Miami; explore a doomed town in the middle of the Everglades; visit what is left of the religious community who dreamed a ten millions city and meet the last survivor of a vanished timber town and his eighty years quest to find his birthplace. Enjoy the ultimate connection between man, land and time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?214261</url></doc>
